# Bucket List Readiness

Use the project skill `bucket-list-readiness` when the user asks about readiness for bucket-list destinations such as Maldives, Raja Ampat, Philippines, Fiji, Komodo, Sipadan, Palau, Socorro, or Galapagos.

When new dive logging or dive Q&A adds material readiness evidence, refresh `bucket-list-readiness.md`, especially:

- `## Bucket list summary`
- `Last updated`
- `## Current snapshot`
- the relevant destination section under `## Bucket list destinations`
- `## Current likely position` when the ranking changes

Do not treat Raja Ampat as a separate readiness system unless the user explicitly asks for a Raja-Ampat-only view.

For dives that took place at a bucket-list destination, update the summary row and destination section in the same workflow after logging and Q&A.
